{"Id":483,"LanguageCodes":["zh","zho"],"Name":"zho-majian1","Author":"Ma Jian","Language":"Chinese(traditional)","Description":"Chinese(traditional)","Direction":"ltr","Source":"http://tanzil.net","Translations":[{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"以時光盟誓，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"一切人確是在虧折之中，"},{"SurahNumber":103,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"惟信道而且行善，并以真理相勸，以堅忍相勉的人則不然。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"傷哉！每個誹謗者, 詆毀者"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"他聚積財產, 而當作武器"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他以為他的財產, 能使他不滅。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"絕不然, 他必定要被投在毀滅坑中。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"你怎能知道毀滅坑是什麼？"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":6,"Text":"是真主的燃著的烈活。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":7,"Text":"能升到人的心上。"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":8,"Text":"他們必定要被關在烈火中"},{"SurahNumber":104,"VerseNumber":9,"Text":"吊在許多很高的柱子上。"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":1,"Text":"難道你不知道你的主怎樣處治象的主人們嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":2,"Text":"難道他沒有使他們的計謀, 變成無益的嗎？"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":3,"Text":"他曾派遣成群的鳥去傷他們"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":4,"Text":"以粘土石射擊他們"},{"SurahNumber":105,"VerseNumber":5,"Text":"使他們變成吃剩的乾草一樣。"}]}